<TEXT>
<P>
Jeff Kent hit a solo home run in the ninth inning to give California a 5-4 
victory over Cal State Fullerton Sunday in a nonconference baseball game at 
Fullerton. 
</P>
<P>
Kent, who attended Edison High School, hit the first pitch off reliever Sam 
Colarusso (2-1) over the left-field fence. It was his first home run of the 
season. 
</P>
